                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3031" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0705</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9569 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电动汽车或燃油汽车？——比亚迪公司的四次战略选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Electric Automobiles or Fuel Cars ?——Byd Co&#39;s Four Strategic Choice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈又星</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略；战略决策；战略演变；资源优化配置</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise strategy; Strategic decision; Strategy evolution;   Resource optimization allocation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪公司从选择手机电池业务起步，仅用不到10年时间就一举成为了全球充电电池生产商的第二名，随后比亚迪公司通过收购陕西秦川汽车第二次战略选择进军汽车整车生产制造行业，仅用3年时间比亚迪汽车销量超过60万辆。2009年比亚迪进行了第三次战略选择，战略方向确定为新能源，包括LED，光伏发电及太阳能等领域。2010年比亚迪公司战略问题集中爆发：经销商退网、公司裁员、汽车销量严重下滑及公司高管辞职等。痛定思痛之后比亚迪公司对其战略进行第四次重新定位：IT、汽车（重点电动汽车、回归传统燃油汽车）及新能源。本案例围绕比亚迪的四次战略选择，研究企业发展中战略得与失，旨在对企业进行战略决策提供借鉴指导。本案例适用本科生及MBA教学的《企业战略管理》课程，尤其是公司层战略决策等方面的案例教学中讨论使用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Byd Co started from the choice of mobile phone battery business.It became the world&#39;s top second producer of rechargeable batteries in less than 10 years. Then Byd Co made the second strategic choice to enter the automobile manufacturing industry through the acquisition of  Shanxi  Qinchuan automobile. BYD car salt  in more than 600 thousand vehicles in just 3 years. Byd Co made third strategic choices in2009.Its strategic direction was identified as new energy sources, including LED, pv power and solar energy and other fields. Byd Co focused on the outbreak of strategic issues in 2010: dealers back network, layoffs, serious decline in car sales and company executives to resign. Byd Co made the fourth re-positioning of the future strategy as a warning: IT, automotive (emphasis on electric vehicles, return to traditional fuel vehicles) and new energy.This case studies the strategic gain and loss in the development of enterprises around BYD&#39;s four strategic choice.The purpose is to provide guidance for enterprises to make strategic decisions.The case applies to undergraduate and MBA teaching &quot;enterprise strategic management&quot; course, especially discussing and using  in the case of strategic decision-making and other aspects.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略选择的环境分析、 SWOT 分析、公司层战略与业务层战略、多元化与一体化战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-11</td>
                            </tr>
